      "\n",
      "### Introduction Hook:\n",
      "\n",
      "Remember those monolithic applications that felt like wrestling an octopus? What if you could break down complex tasks into smaller, intelligent, and collaborative \"digital workers\"? Multi-agent systems (MAS) are doing just that, and they're not just a theoretical concept anymore ‚Äì they're a powerful tool for modern software developers.\n",
      "\n",
      "### Main Sections:\n",
      "\n",
      "**1. Enhanced Modularity and Scalability:**\n",
